{"tid":528470,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"2003應該係近代最sad一年","createTime":"2018-01-13T20:04:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-15T11:51:51.000Z","uid":123774,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c6949d69efd87007ba2f8e77b1d9653b4c5cbf30","tid":528470,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T20:04:38.000Z","msg":"2002年10月羅文<br />\n2003年3月沙士襲港<br />\n2003年4月張國榮<br />\n2003年12月梅艷芳<br />\n<br />\n個年好sad<br />\n仲聽緊羅文幾許風雨懷念時<br />\n突然話哥哥自殺 一開始以為笑話<br />\n然後以為係同名同姓<br />\n<br />\n睇住梅姐講野都唔正開告別演唱會<br />\n佢最後唱住夕陽之歌告別<br />\n<br />\n當年考AL<br />\n無記錯考試要戴口罩<br />\n有諗過oral點算<br />\n點知係邊個講緊野<br />\n<br />\n出街見人咳兩聲就好驚要避開<br />\n左鄰右舍朋友都唔敢見面傾計<br />\n<br />\n2003真係好sad <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"613418b1b7767137fd074d7a7a53f995c65ee25a","tid":528470,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T20:07:25.000Z","msg":"仲記得七一遊行係2003年開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04c30871fb0b24ead2a10a55df5d9a1a0e070ee2","tid":528470,"uid":3549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T01:03:00.000Z","msg":"年年都係咁sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"affd777474ca2062797d20efe1ae7b1761d1166f","tid":528470,"uid":69614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T01:04:11.000Z","msg":"一年比一年sad"},{"pid":"2c9f5acff541f699cfd29e329d59bc43ba62bdc2","tid":528470,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T05:59:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6351b7a81c2c5dd9e44efc5aff06d48133de7602","tid":528470,"uid":137361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T06:02:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e98a4521a5b7737676436f52ce7387ec0bc962ae","tid":528470,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6351b7a81c2c5dd9e44efc5aff06d48133de7602","